+Create scripts/supplier-intelligence.js
+
+Runs nightly at 1 AM via pm2 cron.
+
+1. Query traficos from Supabase grouped by supplier
+2. For each supplier calculate:
+   - Average document turnaround time
+   - Most common missing documents
+   - Average shipment value
+   - T-MEC usage rate
+3. Send to Ollama qwen3:8b for pattern analysis
+4. Write insights to supplier_intelligence table in Supabase
+5. Flag suppliers with degrading performance via notification
+
+This runs free on Ollama every night.
+Compounds weekly — by month 2 CRUZ knows which suppliers
+are slow, which docs they always miss, what to pre-request.

