+   - Day of week
+   - Time of day
+   - Bridge used
+   - Month
+3. Send to Ollama qwen3:8b
+4. Write predictions to crossing_predictions table
+5. Dashboard shows: "Best crossing window: Tuesday 7-9 AM, 
+   avg 2.3 days. Avoid Friday afternoon."
+
+This is proprietary intelligence no competitor has.

